---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import heroPhoto from '../assets/photos/hero.jpg';
---

<section id="hero" class="relative overflow-hidden pt-40 pb-22 px-6 bg-ink text-center">
  <Image
    src={heroPhoto}
    alt=""
    width={1920}
    height={960}
    format="webp"
    quality={75}
    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
    style="filter: grayscale(0.4) brightness(0.34)"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_30%,rgba(13,14,17,.55),rgba(13,14,17,.92))]"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
    <p class="font-label text-azure text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] mb-4">
      For online fitness coaches
    </p>

    <h1 class="font-display text-white leading-[0.92] mb-0 text-[clamp(2.75rem,7vw,5.5rem)]">
      The AI version<br />of <span class="text-azure">you</span>.
    </h1>

    <p class="text-[#CFD2D7] text-lg mt-5 max-w-md text-balance">
      One 30 minute interview becomes an AI that coaches your clients that sounds exactly like
      you, the check-ins, the DMs, the everyday stuff. No content library required.
    </p>

    <div class="w-full max-w-md mt-9 bg-surface-1/85 backdrop-blur-md border border-hairline-dark rounded-[22px] p-5 shadow-2xl text-left">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pb-4 mb-4 border-b border-hairline-dark">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-azure-deep flex items-center justify-center font-display text-white text-base shrink-0">
          S
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-body font-bold text-sm text-text leading-tight">Sarah&rsquo;s AI</p>
          <p class="font-label text-xs text-text-soft">replying to a client &middot; now</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-[85%] bg-surface-2 text-text-soft text-sm leading-relaxed rounded-2xl rounded-bl-[5px] px-4 py-3 mb-3">
        Stuck in a hotel this weekend, only dumbbells in the gym. Can I still get today&rsquo;s
        session in?
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-[86%] ml-auto bg-azure-deep text-white text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed rounded-2xl rounded-br-[5px] px-4 py-3">
        Totally. I&rsquo;ll swap you to today&rsquo;s push day with just dumbbells. Same
        intent, same effort. Sending it over now. Hit me after and tell me how the
        shoulders felt.
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 mt-3 font-label text-xs text-text-soft">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-azure"></span> in their words, on their rules
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-8">
      <a
        href="#early-access"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-azure-deep hover:bg-azure-deep/90 text-white font-bold text-[15.5px] px-7 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors"
      >
        Get early access
      </a>
      <a
        href="#how-it-works"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/6 hover:border-azure border border-hairline-dark text-white font-semibold text-[15.5px] px-7 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors"
      >
        See how it works
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
